  "translations": {
    "en": "He said: Abu Bakr Muhammad ibn Umar al-Ji'abi reported to me, saying: Abu al-Abbas Ahmad ibn Muhammad ibn Sa'id al-Hamdani narrated to us, saying: Ahmad ibn Yahya ibn Zakariyya, and Muhammad ibn Abdullah ibn Muhammad ibn Salim among others, both narrated to us from Abdullah ibn Salim, who said: Hisham ibn Mihran narrated to us, from his maternal uncle Muhammad ibn Zayd al-Attar - who was among the prominent companions of al-A'mash - who said: Muhammad ibn Ahmad ibn al-Hasan narrated to us, who said: Mundhir ibn Jayfar narrated to us, who said: Muhammad ibn Yazid al-Bani narrated to us, saying:",
    "ur": "اسناد: انہوں نے کہا: مجھے ابوبکر محمد بن عمر الجعابی نے خبر دی... محمد بن یزید البانی نے ہم سے بیان کیا:",
    "tr": "İsnad: Ebû Bekir Muhammed b. Ömer el-Ci'âbî bana haber verdi... Muhammed b. Yezîd el-Bânî bize rivayet etti:",
    "fa": "اسناد: ابوبکر محمد بن عمر جعابی به من خبر داد... محمد بن یزید بانی برای ما نقل کرد:",
    "id": "Isnad: Abu Bakr Muhammad bin Umar al-Ji'abi mengabarkan kepadaku... Muhammad bin Yazid al-Bani menceritakan kepada kami:",
    "bn": "ইসনাদ: আবু বকর মুহাম্মাদ ইবনে উমর আল-জি'আবী আমাকে জানালেন... মুহাম্মাদ ইবনে ইয়ায়িদ আল-বানী বর্ণনা করেছেন:",
    "es": "Isnad: Abu Bakr Muhammad ibn Umar al-Yi'abi me informó... Muhammad ibn Yazid al-Bani nos narró:",
    "fr": "Isnad : Abû Bakr Muhammad ibn 'Umar al-Ji'âbî m'a informé... Muhammad ibn Yazîd al-Bânî nous a rapporté :",
    "de": "Isnad: Abū Bakr Muhammad ibn 'Umar al-Dschi'ābī berichtete mir... Muhammad ibn Yazīd al-Bānī berichtete uns:",
    "ru": "Иснад: Абу Бакр Мухаммад ибн Умар аль-Джиъаби сообщил мне... Мухаммад ибн Язид аль-Бани рассказал нам:",
    "zh": "传述链：阿布·伯克尔·穆罕默德·本·欧默尔·杰阿比告诉我…穆罕默德·本·业齐德·巴尼传述给我们："
  }
}